channel.title: Cache editor problem
channel.description:
I've been trying to use toms cache editor, but when I load my cache it doesn't do anything. This is what it looks like. It won't let you click 'file' or 'help', or even exit out of it once you try and load the cache. You have to physically go into the task manager and end the process.
[img]http://i.imgur.com/DGFzXfg.png[/img]
